{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1705-12_188"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Rencontre de l’Himen et de l’Amour]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", décembre 1705 [tome 12], p. 188-193."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Les Vers suivans ont esté faits par un Maître des Comptes, qui n’a pas moins de goust pour la Poësie, que pour les Sciences, & dont l’esprit a souvent brillé dans l’une des Academies établies par Sa Majesté."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "RENCONTRE DE L’HYMEN ET DE L’AMOUR,"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[1]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[2]", "text": "Le jour du Mariage de deux personnes de la premiere distinction dans la Robe."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "L’AMOUR."}], "attributes": {"type": "speaker"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " Où court le Dieu de l’Hymenée ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Et quel est le sujet de son empressement ?"}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "L’HYMEN."}], "attributes": {"type": "speaker"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " Je vais pour accomplir l’heureuse destinée"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "D’un Magistrat illustre, en qui rien ne dément"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "L’éclat de tant d’Ayeux, dont il fait l’ornement ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " Et d’une Epouse fortunée,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Que Themis vit un jour naistre dans son Palais,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Et qui dés ce moment par le Ciel fut ornée,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "D’esprit & de vertu, de graces & d’attraits."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Aujourd’huy, par mes soins, un doux nœud les assemble ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "Au Temple, où l’on m’attend, on doit trouver ensemble"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": " La Foy, la Pudeur, l’Equité,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": " La Sagesse, la Probité,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "Et les autres Vertus que tu ne connois gueres,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[13]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[13]/text()[1]", "text": "Lorsque seul & sans moy tu forges tes mysteres."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[14]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[14]/text()[1]", "text": " Adieu, ne me retarde pas."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "L’AMOUR."}], "attributes": {"type": "speaker"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " Et moy je vôle sur tes pas,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " Je veux estre de la partie ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Cette union sans moy seroit mal assortie :"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Quoy ! peut-on sans l’Amour former de si beaux nœuds ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Et crois-tu qu’ils n’ont pas déja senty mes feux ?"}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "L’HYMEN."}], "attributes": {"type": "speaker"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " Non, ton secours ne m’est pas necessaire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Ton air badin, folastre, indiscret, temeraire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Sieroit mal aux grands cœurs que je vais rendre heureux."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "L’AMOUR."}], "attributes": {"type": "speaker"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Hymen, ignores-tu que je prends, quand je veux ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais avec toy, sur tout, un autre caractere."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Tu me verras discret, tendre, sage & sincere ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " J’auray pour armes ces traits d’or,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui causent sous mes loix les secrettes blessures,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Dont se sentent picquer les ames les plus pures :"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Du flambeau que je tiens, tu verras naistre encor,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "D’innocentes ardeurs, & des feux legitimes,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": " Pour enflamer & l’Epouse & l’Epoux."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "L’HYMEN."}], "attributes": {"type": "speaker"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "À ces conditions l’accord est entre nous ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Que d’Hymen & d’Amour leurs cœurs soient les victimes,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Mêlons de nos flambeaux, & la flâme & l’ardeur,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Unissons-nous, allons consommer leur bonheur."}]}]}]}]}